NAME
    Music::Tag::Amazon - Plugin module for Music::Tag to get information
    from Amazon.com

DESCRIPTION
    This plugin gathers additional information about a track from amazon,
    and updates the Music::Tag object.

    Music::Tag::Amazon must be created by Music::Tag.

INSTALLATION
    To install this module type the following:

       perl Makefile.PL
       make
       make test
       make install

DEPENDENCIES
    This module requires these other modules and libraries:

       Music::Tag
       Cache::FileCache
       Encode
       LWP
       Net::Amazon

    I strongly recommend the following to allow proximity matches:

       Lingua::EN::Inflect
       Lingua::Stem
       Text::LevenshteinXS
       Text::Unaccent 

